for $6.60/year!) all the way up to 8GB (for only $12.20/month!)</p><p>These systems are in the Netherlands (Naaldwijk).</p><p>HostSailor is registered in Dubai, UAE (IBM/03/14/8150).&nbsp; You can find their <a href=\"https://www.hostmem.com/tos\">TOS</a> on their website and you can pay with&nbsp;Bitcoin, altcoins, PayPal,&nbsp;Bank Transfer , PaySafeCard, Skrill, WebMoney,&nbsp;Qiwi, Alipay, Western Union, MoneyGram, and Perfect Money.</p><p>Please comment below about your experiences with HostSailor if you decide to take advantage of these great offers!</p><p><strong>Here\u2019s what they had to say:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><em>\u201cHostSailor.com has established itself as a trusted provider of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://hostsailor.com/vps-hosting/\">VPS hosting</a>,<a href=\"https://hostsailor.com/dedicated-servers/\">, Dedicated Servers</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://hostsailor.com/domain-registration/\">Domains</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://hostsailor.com/ssl-certificates/\">SSL certificates</a>, and a variety of other hosting and complementary technology services. HostSailor.com is a truly global company with a unique focus on our customers.\u201d</em></p><p><strong>Now read more to see the offer!</strong></p><p><span id=\"more-25603\"></span></p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>KVM Offer</b></p><ul><li>512MB RAM</li><li>512MB Swap</li><li>1x vCPU Intel(R) Xeon(R) CPU E31240 @ 3.30GHz</li><li>15 GB HDD space<br>\n(Free Double Storage Available)</li><li>512 GB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>/64 IPv6</li><li>KVM/SolusVM</li><li>$1.00 USD/mo</li><li>$3.00 USD/3m</li><li>$6.00 USD/6m</li><li>$12.00 USD/12m</li><li>[<a href=\"https://clients.hostsailor.com/cart.php?gid=37\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Check out all the KVM plans</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Xen Offer</strong></p><ul><li>512MB RAM</li><li>512MB Swap</li><li>1x vCPU Intel(R) Xeon(R